query:
WITH entities AS (
            SELECT *
            FROM bria_payouts
            WHERE account_id = $1 AND wallet_id = $2
            ORDER BY created_at DESC                
            OFFSET $3) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: Repo__Id", e.sequence, e.event, CASE WHEN $4 THEN e.context ELSE NULL::jsonb END as "context: es_entity::ContextData", e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN bria_payout_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.created_at desc, i.id, e.sequence
